# This directory stores trained model artifacts and experiment logs.
# Contents:
#   xgboost_model.pkl       — primary prediction model
#   rf_model.pkl            — random forest (for SHAP comparison)
#   isoforest_model.pkl     — anomaly detection model
#   feature_scaler.pkl      — StandardScaler fitted on training set
#   feature_importance.json — global SHAP feature importances
#   experiments.csv         — experiment tracking (hyperparams, metrics)
#   sleepsense.db           — SQLite database
